            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caisari Divi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Augusto <lb n="3"/>pontifici maximo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> XI <lb n="4"/>tribunicia <expan><abbr>potestat</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> XI </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Neroni Claudio Divi <lb n="2"/>Claudii <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Germanici Caisaris <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epoti</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> Caisaris <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> pro <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epoti</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Divi Augusti ab <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epoti</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Caisari <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> Germanico <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berio</ex></expan> Claudio Drusi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Caisari Augusto <lb n="3"/>Germanico pontifici <lb n="4"/>maximo tribunicia <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> II </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Iuliae Au<supplied reason="lost">gustae</supplied> Agri<supplied reason="lost">ppinae</supplied> Germanic<supplied reason="lost">i Caisaris <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan></supplied> divi Cla<supplied reason="lost">udi uxori</supplied> </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Aenatores tubicines liticines cornicines Romani <lb n="2"/>Romani
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Letzte Zeile: Romani: Nach G. Alföldy vielleicht zugegipst worden, nachdem die vierte Kolumne entstanden war und aus Symmetriegründen &amp;quot;&amp;quot;Romani&amp;quot;&amp;quot; unter diese Kolumne gemeißelt wurde. Genauere Datierung nach G. Alföldy: zwischen 13. Oktober (oder 4. Dezember) 55 n. Chr. und 12. Oktober (oder 3. Dezember) 56 n. Chr. Ursprünglich aus drei Tafeln zusammengesetzt als Verkleidung einer breiten Statuenbasis in opus coementicium (obige Maßangaben beziehen sich auf die Gesamtmaße der Basis). Maße der einzelnen Tafeln: 1. (aus 47 Fragmenten zusammengesetzt): 75 x 213 x 35; 2. (aus 19 Fragmenten zusammengesetzt): 75 x 139 x 35; 3. (aus 8 Fragmenten zusammengesetzt): 75 x 70 x 38.</p>
            </div>
